{"id":161666,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/澳广-大批军警部署增城制止骚乱/","date":"2011-06-16T10:00:19Z","modified":"2011-06-16T10:00:19Z","title":"澳广 | 大批军警部署增城制止骚乱","content":"<div>\n<p>2011 年 06 月 14 日</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3243056.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/decrease.gif\" alt=\"Decrease\" title=\"Decrease\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3243056.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/standard.gif\" alt=\"Standard\" title=\"Standard\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3243056.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/increase.gif\" alt=\"Increase\" title=\"Increase\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.abc.net.au/cgi-bin/common/mailto/mailto-nojs_query.pl?http://www.abc.net.au/ra/chinese/articles/s3243056.htm&#038;presname=/ra\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/email.gif\" alt=\"Email\" title=\"Email\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.abc.net.au/cgi-bin/common/printfriendly.pl?http://www.abc.net.au/ra/chinese/articles/s3243056.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/print.gif\" alt=\"Print\" title=\"Print\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3243056.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/favourite.gif\" alt=\"Favourite\" title=\"Favourite\" /></a></p>\n<p>据香港媒体报道，中国广州增城市新塘镇在连续三晚发生骚乱后，当局向该市派驻了大批军警。</p>\n<p>报道称，武警13日在最先发生骚乱的大敦村外设置了围栏，并封锁了曾被冲击的派出所。</p>\n<p>电视画面显示，增城市内有许多军队和武警的车辆活动，当地通往广州的一段国道有的围栏被推翻。</p>\n<p>有网民上载视频，显示新塘镇星期天晚上仍有群众聚集破坏，一些汽车被推翻，是当地连续第三晚爆发冲突。</p>\n<p>星期天早些时候，广州市政府召开新闻发布会称，警方出动警力采取果断措施，有效控制了在广东增城市新塘镇发生的骚乱。</p>\n<p>官方的说法是，骚乱起因涉及四川籍孕妇王联梅三天前在街上摆卖遭到驱赶，继而引发骚乱，至少25人被捕。</p>\n<p>增城市市长叶牛平称，新塘骚乱为一起“个别群众与治保人员纠纷引发的聚众滋事事件”，据称被打小贩的丈夫唐学才也出席了新闻发布会，并称妻子和胎儿“都没事”。</p>\n<p>但是外省民工指称，地方治安队长期对商户小贩勒索保护费，并借故殴打外省民工，引起民愤。</p>\n</p></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.radioaustralia.net.au%2Fchinese%2Farticles%2Fs3243056.htm&#038;title=%E5%A4%A7%E6%89%B9%E5%86%9B%E8%AD%A6%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%A2%9E%E5%9F%8E%E5%88%B6%E6%AD%A2%E9%AA%9A%E4%B9%B1\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}